Backend for login authentication with JWT

initialize project
npm init
gitignore
install express
install nodemon as devdependency
install cors - cors setup
install dotenv - create env variables
install cookieParser

connect to mongodb database

built-in middlewares:
express.json for body parsing
serve static files => express.static

create routes
-root
-user
-auth

setup application routes in server.js

create models
-User model

create controller
-user functions => getAllusers, createNewUSer
-auth functions => login, refresh, logout
  -with bcrypt, jwt for access token and refresh token with env secrets

create server.js


FE-
go to client and test login api created.
